---

<Layout 
  title={`Concrete Contractors in ${city}, FL | Driveways, Patios & Slabs`}
  description={`Trusted concrete contractors serving ${city}, Florida. Expert driveway, patio, and slab installation for the Citrus County seat. Call ${phone} for a free quote!`}
  canonical="/locations/inverness/"
>
  <section class="service-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Concrete Contractors in {city}, Florida</h1>
      <p>Professional concrete installation serving {city} and all of {county}. Quality work from experienced local contractors.</p>
      <a href={`tel:${phoneTel}`} class="btn btn-primary">Call {phone}</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-grid">
        <div class="intro-content">
          <h2>Trusted Concrete Services in {city}</h2>
          <p>As the county seat of Citrus County, {city} combines small-town charm with modern amenities. From the historic downtown along the Withlacoochee State Trail to the beautiful lakefront properties on Lake Henderson and the Tsala Apopka Chain of Lakes, Inverness offers diverse living options—each with unique concrete needs.</p>
          
          <p>Brooksville Concrete Co. has built strong relationships with Inverness homeowners over the years. Located just a short drive from our Hernando County base, we serve Inverness with the same quality and professionalism that's made us a trusted name throughout the Nature Coast.</p>
          
          <p>Whether you need a new driveway for your lakeside home, a patio to enjoy Inverness's beautiful weather, or a foundation for a backyard workshop, our experienced team delivers results that exceed expectations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-content">
          <h3>Our {city} Services</h3>
          <ul class="why-list">
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Concrete Driveways</strong>
                Long-lasting driveways for Inverness homes, from standard finishes to decorative stamped concrete.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Patios & Outdoor Living</strong>
                Beautiful concrete patios perfect for enjoying Inverness's mild climate year-round.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Lakefront Concrete</strong>
                Specialized solutions for properties on the Tsala Apopka Chain and Lake Henderson.
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
              <div>
                <strong>Slabs & Foundations</strong>
                Solid foundations for sheds, garages, workshops, and outbuildings.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="service-content">
    <h2>Why {city} Homeowners Choose Us</h2>
    
    <p>Inverness has a character all its own. The historic downtown, the beautiful lakes, the Withlacoochee State Trail running through town—it's a special place to live. Your concrete work should reflect that same quality. We take pride in delivering results that enhance Inverness properties and stand up to Florida's demanding conditions.</p>

    <h3>Lakefront Property Expertise</h3>
    
    <p>Many Inverness homes sit on the shores of Lake Henderson or along the Tsala Apopka Chain of Lakes. These waterfront properties present specific challenges for concrete work. Higher water tables, fluctuating lake levels, and the need for erosion-resistant installations all factor into our approach.</p>
    
    <p>For lakefront driveways and patios, we use techniques that account for these conditions—proper grading for drainage, appropriate concrete thicknesses, and reinforcement designed for the specific soil conditions of your property.</p>

    <h3>Historic Downtown and Established Neighborhoods</h3>
    
    <p>Inverness's downtown area and surrounding established neighborhoods often feature older homes with aging concrete that needs replacement. We work carefully in these areas, respecting the character of the neighborhood while delivering modern, durable concrete surfaces.</p>
    
    <p>Driveway replacements in established areas require careful planning—coordinating with utility locations, managing access during construction, and ensuring the finished product complements your home's style. Our experienced crews handle these details professionally.</p>

    <h3>Quality Materials for Lasting Results</h3>
    
    <p>Every Inverness project uses premium materials designed for longevity:</p>
    
    <ul>
      <li><strong>4,000+ PSI concrete</strong> — Significantly stronger than code minimum</li>
      <li><strong>Fiber reinforcement</strong> — Helps prevent surface cracking</li>
      <li><strong>Proper joint spacing</strong> — Accommodates expansion and contraction</li>
      <li><strong>Quality sealers</strong> — Protects against staining and weathering</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Serving All of {city}</h3>
    
    <p>From downtown Inverness to the rural areas of eastern Citrus County, we serve the entire community. Whether you're near the historic courthouse, out by Whispering Pines Park, or in one of the many neighborhoods that make Inverness home, we're ready to tackle your concrete project.</p>
    
    <p>Contact Brooksville Concrete Co. for your free Inverness estimate. Call <a href={`tel:${phoneTel}`}>{phone}</a> or complete our online form to get started.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Quality Concrete for {city} Properties</h2>
      <p>Free estimates for homes throughout {county}</p>
      <a href={`tel:${phoneTel}`} class="btn">Call {phone} Now</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
